Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.36,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:59.70,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}傷を負った　世界を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:04.71,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}強く儚い果実
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:11.63,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}つきまとう　責任の重たさで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:16.14,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}熟れ落ちて　土へと還る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:19.06,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.91,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:26.02,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}この血の滾りを解放してけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:27.12,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}そこにいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:32.04,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}衝突に戦々恐々　降り立つ堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:37.30,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}早々に早熟な実も　食らい尽くすの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:43.01,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}もがく度に　蒼穹に聴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:46.12,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}君を確かめた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:46.95,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}あっけない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.85,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}無い無い　馴れ合い　有り余った慟哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:56.19,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}葛藤に混乱していく　今を生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:03:03.07,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)\pos(960,3)}それでもまだ　僕らは目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:04.52,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)\fs45\pos(960,54)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
